---
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import mbbsImg from "@assets/img/mbbs.jpg";
import GeorgiaImg from "@assets/img/GeorgiaImg2.jpg";
---

<section>
  <div class="united-stats-area pt-120">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="united-states">
            <style>
              .text-center {
                text-align: center !important;
              }

              .tab-pane {
                display: none;
              }
              .tab-pane.active {
                display: block;
              }
              .nav-tabs {
                flex-direction: column;
              }
              .nav-tabs .nav-link {
                border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
                border-radius: 0.25rem;
                margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
              }
              .nav-tabs .nav-link.active {
                background-color: #007bff;
                color: white;
              }
            </style>

            <h2 class="united-states__title mb-15">MBBS IN GEORGIA: Eligibility, Colleges, Fees, and Examinations</h2>

            <p>
                Georgia has emerged as a prominent destination for pursuing an MBBS degree, offering high-quality education
                 with globally recognized degrees. Renowned medical universities in Georgia attract students from around the world due to their modern facilities, experienced faculty, and affordable tuition fees.
            </p>
            <p>
                A degree in MBBS from Georgia opens doors to diverse career opportunities in medicine, including specialization, research, and healthcare administration. Graduates often 
                find themselves well-prepared for competitive residency programs globally.
            </p>

            <p>
                Embark on your journey towards becoming a skilled medical professional with MBBS in Georgia. Explore the rich cultural heritage of Georgia while receiving top-notch medical education that sets you on a path to success in the field of medicine.
            </p>
    

          </div>
         
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <Image src={GeorgiaImg} alt="Australia Image" width="600" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
